headline: Caterpillar Inc. to Announce First-Quarter 2025 Financial Results on April 30
summary: Caterpillar Inc. (NYSE: CAT) will release first-quarter 2025 financial results at 5:30 a.m. CDT on Wednesday, April 30. The full text of the release will be available at investors.caterpillar.com/financials/quarterly-results and on PR Newswire. The release will be furnished to the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) via a Current Report on Form 8-K in compliance with applicable SEC rules.
